## Project Overview

Create a semantic SDK layer above the existing generic execute function which executes raw GraphQL queries in the monday.com JavaScript SDK. The semantic layer should provide high-level, intuitive methods for common CRUD operations on boards, items, and columns.

## User Requirements

Based on your request, you want:

- Multiple new files introducing a semantic layer
- New methods on boards, items, and columns
- CRUD capabilities: createItem, fetchItem/s, createBoard, getBoard, updateItemColumnValues, getColumns, createColumn, updateColumn

## Success Criteria

- Complete CRUD coverage for boards, items, and columns
- Type safety with TypeScript definitions
- Backward compatibility with existing SDK
- Clear, intuitive API design

